text: Lawrence "Larry" Page (born March 26, 1973) is an American computer scientist, Internet entrepreneur, and business magnate He co-founded Google with Sergey Brin. Page was born in East Lansing, Michigan. ==References== Category:Google Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:American computer scientists Category:Google people Category:Businesspeople from Michigan Category:American chief executives Category:American company founders
